---
import Layout from '../layouts/Landing.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Fundament">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <h1 class="about-hero-title">About Fundament</h1>
    <p class="about-hero-body">
      Fundament is software for running an Autonomous Private Cloud. It is designed to provide
      organizations with a minimal, reliable foundation for running modern applications. Unlike
      traditional platforms that bundle every service by default, Fundament is basic at its &mdash;
      delivering only the essential infrastructure and orchestration layers &mdash; while allowing
      each tenant to extend their environment with exactly the services and tools they they need.
    </p>
    <p class="about-hero-body">
      On top of this foundation, Fundament serves as an internal developer platform (IDP): enabling
      developers to build, deploy, and operate applications with speed and confidence. Its API-first
      design, multi-tenant architecture, and focus on autonomy and scalability make it suitable for
      organizations that want cloud capabilities on their own terms; secure, reliable, and without
      unnecessary complexity.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
      <h2 class="about-section-title">Project status</h2>
      <p class="about-section-subtitle">Concept &amp; Development</p>
      <p class="about-section-body">
        The focus of the project is currently on research and ideation. Some initial PoC
        applications may be built to give shape to ideas and to provide early feedback from testing
        users.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
      <h2 class="about-section-title">Organization</h2>
      <p class="about-section-body">
        Fundament is being developed by <a href="https://digilab.overheid.nl/" target="_blank"
          >Digilab</a
        >. Digilab is a technical innovation team and testing environment initiated by the Dutch
        government to facilitate secure, responsible, and standardized data sharing across public
        sector organizations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  @reference "../styles/global.css";

  .about-hero {
    @apply py-primitives-space-64 px-primitives-space-32 mx-auto max-w-200;
  }
  .about-hero-title {
    @apply text-display-2 font-display mb-primitives-space-24 text-content m-0 font-medium tracking-[-0.02em];
  }
  .about-hero-body {
    @apply text-body-lg font-body text-content mb-primitives-space-16 m-0 max-w-180 font-normal;
  }
  .about-hero-body:last-child {
    @apply mb-0;
  }

  .about-section {
    @apply border-dividers border-t;
  }
  .about-section-inner {
    @apply py-primitives-space-48 px-primitives-space-32 mx-auto max-w-200;
  }
  .about-section-title {
    @apply text-display-4 font-display text-accent-600 mb-primitives-space-8 m-0 font-medium tracking-[-0.01em];
  }
  .about-section-subtitle {
    @apply text-body-lg font-body text-content mb-primitives-space-8 m-0 font-medium;
  }
  .about-section-body {
    @apply text-body-lg font-body text-content m-0 max-w-180 font-normal;
  }
</style>
